  "excerpt": "<p>Hi friends! I have added a whole new line of items to my shop and I wanted you to be the first to know! I’m selling vinyl decals made of commercial grade vinyl for all your laptop, car, water bottle needs. They’re adorable, fun and ready for you to see below!</p>\n",
  "content": "<p>Hi friends! I have added a whole new line of items to my shop and I wanted you to be the first to know! I’m selling vinyl decals made of commercial grade vinyl for all your laptop, car, water bottle needs. They’re adorable, fun and ready for you to see below!</p>\n<p>You may remember my preview mockup pic in my last post with a sneak peek of designs, but now they’re <a href=\"/\">available in my shop for purchase</a> and you can see what they look like in real life. Many of the designs have both large and mini decal versions available, and some are designs you will recognize from my tote bags and ornaments! What can I say, I like when things coordinate. 🙂</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/new-vinyl-decals/fullsizeoutput-72f5-1.jpeg\" alt width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/new-vinyl-decals/fullsizeoutput-72f6-2.jpeg\" alt width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/new-vinyl-decals/fullsizeoutput-72f7-3.jpeg\" alt width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>How cute are the cacti? Those were designed by Hubby. 😉 My favorite (and best selling by far) is Cat Mom! Currently making Dog Mom/Dad ones too, don’t worry.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-10147 post__image\" src=\"/posts/new-vinyl-decals/fullsizeoutput-997d-4.jpeg\" alt width=\"980\" height=\"653\"></p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/new-vinyl-decals/fullsizeoutput-995e-5.jpeg\" alt width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/new-vinyl-decals/fullsizeoutput-9964-6.jpeg\" alt width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/new-vinyl-decals/fullsizeoutput-9966-7.jpeg\" alt width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p>There are a few different Philly related designs, and even some emojis because everyone loves a good heart eyes stuck on their fave notebook, right?</p>\n<div class=\"post__gallery\"><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/new-vinyl-decals/fullsizeoutput-9951-8.jpeg\" alt width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div><div class=\"post__gallery-item\">\n          <img class=\"post__gallery-image post__image\" src=\"/posts/new-vinyl-decals/fullsizeoutput-9969-9.jpeg\" alt width=\"600\" height=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n        </div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><a href=\"/\">Check out my storefront to see the rest of my vinyl decals and grab one for yourself,</a> and let me know below which one is your favorite!</p>\n",
